<ul><li>\(\beta\)&nbsp;particles produce&nbsp;<b>wispy tracks</b>, as they are&nbsp;<b>easily deflected</b>&nbsp;as a result of collisions with air molecules.<br></li><li>Tracks are not as visible because&nbsp;\(\beta\)&nbsp;particles are&nbsp;<b>less ionising&nbsp;</b>than&nbsp;\(\alpha\)&nbsp;particles.</li></ul>